  <brief_title>Immediate Versus Delayed Induction in Term-PROM Using or Not Antibiotic Prophylaxis</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of Antibiotic Prophylaxis in Immediate Versus Delayed Induction in Term-PROM - a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
